graph TB
    subgraph "Zero Trust Architecture"
        User[User + Device] --> IDP[Identity Provider<br/>Authenticate]
        IDP --> Policy[Policy Engine<br/>Authorize Every Request]
        Policy --> Proxy[Access Proxy<br/>mTLS, Encrypted]
        Proxy --> SvcA[Service A]
        Proxy --> SvcB[Service B]
        Proxy --> SvcC[Service C]
    end

    SvcA <-->|mTLS| SvcB
    SvcB <-->|mTLS| SvcC

    Note[Never trust,<br/>always verify]

    style Policy fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff
